message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been valued at $12000 by you. Considering its unique features and benefits, I believe it would be a valuable addition to your collection. I am offering this exceptional item to you at an exclusive price of $11000. This is a special opportunity for you to acquire it at a significant discount compared to its market value. Please let me know if you're interested in proceeding with the purchase.
